# ============================================================
#  Data — NEVER commit (multi-GB, and the papers are copyrighted).
#  Each machine downloads these locally; see PROJECT_MAP.md.
# ============================================================
data/raw/
data/processed/
papers/
analysis/
results/figures/*.png
*.rds
*.rds.gz
*.mat
*.mtx
*.npz
*.npy
*.h5ad
*.zip

# keep the small committed bits inside the ignored trees:
!data/README.md
!results/figures/
!results/tables/
!results/tables/.gitkeep

# ---- scratch / local / IDE ----
_archive_DELETE_ME/
.idea/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.tmp
.~lock*#
.Rhistory

# ============================================================
#  KEPT in the repo: all code (src/**: *.py, *.R, *.js),
#  the signatures (signatures/*.txt + README.md),
#  docs/ (primer PDF, deck, email, html source),
#  results/tables/ small CSVs + .gitkeep, data/README.md,
#  PROJECT_MAP.md, src/CODING_PLAN.md, src/README.md.
#  NOTE: results/figures/*.png are NOT committed (regenerated by the pipeline).
# ============================================================
